sources.title: Door To The Other Side | Full Mystery Horror Movie | Happy Halloween!
sources.description:
Door To The Other Side - Tim has lived as a shut-in for years. When a young couple attempts to help re-socialize their recluse neighbor, they unleash a sinister force that preys upon the people who get close to him.
2016. Stars: Nicholas Bianchi, Robin De Lano, Leann Donovan
